      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape, ready for many more adventures. It\u2019s been well-loved and consistently maintained, so it's running beautifully. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that still looks great and drives even better, this is the one! I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm super happy to chat and tell you more about it!",
