    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example utilizes the Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission, providing direct engagement and precise torque transfer to the rear-mounted variable M differential lock. The chassis maintains excellent torsional rigidity, with the rear subframe having undergone a preventative reinforcement procedure. Recent maintenance includes a valve clearance adjustment and a cooling system refresh with an upgraded aluminum radiator. The suspension retains its original geometry with fresh bushings, ensuring the communicative steering and neutral handling balance the E46 chassis is celebrated for. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with enthusiast use, the drivetrain and powertrain remain in robust operating condition.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
