    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered here is a meticulously cared-for vehicle that perfectly bridges the gap between a daily driver and a collector's piece. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood consistent with light highway use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the leather upholstery remains supple with only gentle creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014functions flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is tidy, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule. It has recently undergone a full inspection, including a fresh oil service and brake pad replacement. The car tracks straight, shifts through gears with crisp precision, and provides a quiet, confident ride. This is an honest, well-documented example from a smoke-free home, ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately without any deferred maintenance concerns.",
